ophat Defender comes standard with an LS3, LT1 or LT4 V8 engine, ranging from just over 400 to almost 700 horsepower, or more if clients so desire. The standard suspension of a Defender is not known for its comfort, precision and roadholding, so to keep the driving experience both enjoyable and safe, every Tophat Defender comes standard with a custom designed air suspension system including Koni shock absorbers, large AP Racing brakes and enforced internals from the gearbox through the transfer case and differentials to the drive shafts.[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image=\"139\" img_size=\"full\" el_class=\"unique_approchimg\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"font_roboto\"]With our in-house designers constantly working on new ideas to improve our products, hands-on experience from out technicians who build the cars and close relationships with our customers, valuable feedback is used to implement new ideas and developments to further enhance our vehicles. Make sure to follow us or allow us to keep you up to date about our latest developments.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"home_bg_sec\" css=\".vc_custom_1659199385667{background-image: url(http://localhost/projects/tophatclassics/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/im_banner_logo-1.png?id=143) !important;}\"][vc_column][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Media', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '33-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-07-30 18:04:14', '2022-07-30 18:04:14', '', 33, 'http://localhost/projects/tophatclassics/?p=179', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
